# Conversation State Schema

```json
{
  "user_id": "string",
  "channel": "messenger | whatsapp | insta",
  "current_flow": "string",
  "data": {
    "product_interest": "string | null",
    "identified_price": "float | null",
    "is_credit_qualified": "boolean | null",
    "delivery_data": {
       "full_name": "string",
       "phone": "string",
       "city": "string"
    },
    "tradein_device": {
       "model": "string",
       "battery": "int",
       "grade": "string"
    }
  },
  "metadata": {
    "last_intent": "string",
    "message_count": "int",
    "is_handed_off": "boolean"
  }
}
```
